        <!-- Result Section (Shown after YES) -->
        <div id="resultSection" class="result-container hidden">
            <h1>You Made My Day, <span class="name-highlight">Kaye</span>! üíñ</h1>
            <div class="thank-you">Thank You So Much, My Love! üíå</div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>My Dearest Kaye,</p>
                <p>You have no idea how incredibly happy you've made me by saying YES! From the moment I met you, my world has been brighter, fuller, and more beautiful. You're not just my Valentine, you're the person who makes every day feel special.</p>
                <p>I cherish your smile, your laughter, your kindness, and the way you make everything around you better. Today, and every day, I want to celebrate the amazing person you are.</p>
                <p>Thank you for being you, Kaye. Thank you for saying yes. I promise to make this Valentine's Day as wonderful as you are.</p>
                <p>With all my love and heart,</p>
                <p>Your Secret Admirer üíï</p>
